description:
A DLC pack for GROOVE COASTER WAI WAI PARTY!!!! that includes 10 arranged songs, navigators, and avatars from Touhou Project 〜Imperishable Night!

This pack includes the following content.
■Song Pack (10 songs)
・Finder
・JINGAI CRISIS
・Echoed Bonds
・Guru ☆ Nation
・Bubble no Jumon ha Shu! Po! Push!
・Cinderella Cage
・Gensouno tabibitohe ～ Catch the Heart
・Help me, ERINNNNNN!!
・Ephemeral, Great and Splendid Land of Grief
・？？？（Secret）

■Navigator
・Udongein
・Mokou

■Avatar
・REIMU(3D)
・MARISA(3D)
・UDONGEIN(2D)
・KEINE(2D)

*Some content will be unlocked via missions after downloading.
name: Touhou Project Arrangements Pack 3
